The code presented in this project generates the figures from the paper "Optimising Diversity in Classifier Ensembles". 
See:
https://link.springer.com/epdf/10.1007/s42979-022-01063-7?sharing_token=a7EJqC2mbdmMXC9Ei3AoSve4RwlQNchNByi7wbcMAY4RjxfJwpYT9d1e1JCSjvaiVUHNnDF-BXIht_ugxxEhobCm7G-KA_Q8LTkoJ34L_M8uwV51tB1ht9aFvElFiEaFYKVrRDNgHcrxEhlFa0vUGqsPabCbbr1VUbo-MNkUeqk%3D

The random_splits.py program generates the curves from Figure 1.
The contour_plots.py program generates the contour plots from Figure 2.

More code will be added soon.
